snippet.title: Danny Trejo, Amber Heard, Michelle Rodriguez, Sofia Vergara  -- MACHETE KILLS -- Trailer #2
snippet.description:
God bless Robert Rodriguez for unleashing the crazy in MACHETE KILLS by enlisting Hollywood's most wanted: Mel Gibson AND Charlie Sheen? Stunt casting aside, Rodriguez knows how to please his people by offering the kind of diversity eschewed by most Hollywood films: Danny Trejo, Jessica Alba, Amber Heard, Sofia Vergara, Demian Bichir, Cuba Gooding, Jr., Lady Gaga and more.

Set to open October 11, let the grind of this house blow up the screen! 

Trailer courtesy of Open Road Films.

#machetekills #whoareyouwatching
